title: Changes to Upper Columbia River fall chinook salmon fishery (State of Washington)
text: ( Source : State of Washington ) Actions:Liberalize chinook salmon rules for the mainstem Columbia River upstream from Priest Rapids Dam . Species affected: Chinook salmon . Effective date : Oct. 17 through Nov . 30 , 2015 Location:Mainstem Columbia
